OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night with a few
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,8,Fnorth. Conditions will be rather murky
OL,9,Faround eastern coasts for a time this
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny early morning rain
OL,13,Fquickly clearing away. Otherwise a
OL,14,Fbright day with sunny spells and a few
OL,15,Fscattered showers, one or two possibly
OL,16,Fon the heavy side in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
